<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcf778278-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0" identifier="/us/usc/t48/s1428c"><num value="1428c">§ 1428c.</num><heading> Accounting procedures</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The plan provided for in <ref href="/us/usc/t48/s1428a">section 1428a of this title</ref> shall set forth such fiscal control and fund accounting procedures as may be necessary to assure proper disbursement, repayment, and accounting for such funds.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcf778279-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/601/s5">Pub. L. 90–601, § 5</ref>, <date date="1968-10-17">Oct. 17, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/1172">82 Stat. 1172</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idcf77827a-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idcf77827b-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="idcf77827c-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was not enacted as part of the Organic Act of Guam which comprises this chapter.</p>
</note>
</notes>
